The paper proposes a new method for crowd flow prediction using a Spatial-Temporal Self-Attention Network. This involves the use of deep learning techniques such as CNN/GCN and LSTM, which are commonly used in the fields of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the use of attention mechanisms, which are commonly used in the fields of information retrieval (cs.IR) and social intelligence (cs.SI). Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper are cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.SI, and cs.IR.
